status_message: You were a father to the whole neighborhood. I'm trying to live up to your example.

Thank You, Louisville!

Jada & I just left the the Celebration of The G.O.A.T. We have never experienced a more warm & loving town. You sent the Champ off right! We are honored and humbled by your unity, your spirit and your gracious hospitality!

Our deepest love & respect go out to the family, friends & community of one of the most beautiful souls we've ever met.

Louisville... We Shall Return!

You shook up the World!
My Mentor & My Friend.
You changed my Life. 
Rest in Peace.
